Class XmlCompare

    Cloneable

    public class XmlCompare
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task
    Ant task for comparing two XML documents. Ignores whitespace as well as ordering of element attributes in determining equivalence. Examples: 
      <xmlcompare file1="./file_one.xml" file2="./file_two.xml" >
    Performs the comparison on file_one.xml versus file_two.xml. Fails the build with a message identifying the discrepancy if the two documents are not equivalent.
